f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2416fcde9bab3767db6007a6e1346b084aa0a7df","tid":1249756,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"拉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4251bf41a776355fe6382b4c6a972d4772154203","tid":1249756,"uid":246087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:52:10.000Z","msg":"疏忽照顧兒童啦，明知自己工作好多時候唔係固定返工放工，又唔揾多個大人/請個工人去照顧<br />\n<br />\n知法犯法"},{"pid":"e7e1ff8c5178c40dc06fc74048f4c6101b166b1d","tid":1249756,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:53:13.000Z","msg":"又告得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33314fd6c5e1730ea1a561e11704f68b9420e922","tid":1249756,"uid":240425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"310b9f4be4fa58965b30a7a0be5ea791570ce648","tid":1249756,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f8e3e16c8f67c2241cc7ec11966e241c0b320e","tid":1249756,"uid":21095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"693919c5634b499ec96af216a697bcb1f76d46e0","tid":1249756,"uid":96715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:43:09.000Z","msg":"第212章 《侵害人身罪條例》<br />\n27.對所看管兒童或少年人虐待或忽略<br />\n(1)任何超過16歲而對不足該年歲的任何兒童或少年人負有管養、看管或照顧責任的人，如<span style=\"color: blue;\">故意</span>襲擊、虐待、忽略、拋棄或遺棄該兒童或少年人，或導致、促致該兒童或少年人受襲擊、虐待、<span style=\"color: red;\">忽略</span>、拋棄或遺棄，其方式相當<span style=\"color: red;\">可能導致該兒童或少年人受到不必要的苦楚或健康損害(包括視力、聽覺的損害或喪失，肢體、身體器官的傷損殘缺，或精神錯亂)</span>，即屬犯可循公訴程序審訊的罪行 &mdash;&mdash;  (由1991年第50號第4條修訂)<br />\n(a)循公訴程序定罪後，可處監禁10年；或  (由1950年第22號附表修訂；由1995年第68號第51條修訂)<br />\n(b)循簡易程序定罪後，可處監禁3年，  (由1995年第68號第51條修訂)<br />\n而就本條而言，凡超過16歲而對不足該年歲的任何兒童或少年人負有管養、看管或照顧責任的父母或其他人，如沒有為該兒童或少年人提供足夠的食物、衣物或住宿，或如本身不能以其他方式提供該等食物、衣物或住宿，卻明知及故意不採取步驟，向負責提供衣食住予有需要的兒童或少年人的主管當局、社團或機構取得此等供給，即當作忽略該兒童或少年人而其方式相當可能導致該兒童或少年人的健康受損害。<br />\n<br />\n佢條件係故意<br />\n不過佢話老公唔得閒<br />\n推理上好大可能佢本身未放工既時候已經無人睇住個仔<br />\n再查一查就知嗰d時間係咪無人睇住個仔<br />\n就可以prove到係故意<br />\n係無人睇既話就告到佢?<br />\n<br />\n利申 非讀law求law撚解釋<br />\n附上link一條<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5JuWTsprD7o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5JuWTsprD7o&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PrzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=6d9ba226\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5JuWTsprD7o</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:14:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f400a6e4a0975a4e93650f048037488320be546f","tid":1249756,"uid":175996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"pushh"},{"pid":"5b5bd0fe371bd89d7e769eddf199130f654ac7cb","tid":1249756,"uid":258181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"佢老公唔識送個女去醫院洗腸嘅咩？"},{"pid":"0f5c051e26dbe6770c1f96a64d528ebabaed43d7","tid":1249756,"uid":266148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"我一聽就覺得係作故仔想d爸爸媽媽或長期病患家屬同情，然後指責示威者不是"},{"pid":"ced8905f0c291d503fbc318a4efcaaa023d10ff0","tid":1249756,"uid":150536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae93561b5b3727a79bab491a72d7b521110d5278","tid":1249756,"uid":73621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49bef37082faeff8e70f1d1a009e64cb39f0145a","tid":1249756,"uid":36174,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T0